{"tid":2076596,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"《華富村女鬼的考驗》","createTime":"2020-06-23T15:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T15:35:04.000Z","uid":281374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"055fc76ad67e4c641c0fb7e85e1911bd5857ae1a","tid":2076596,"uid":281374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 《華富村女鬼的考驗》</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k3OPJVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk3OPJVY.jpg&h=d4183320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據說在80年代，有一個長得像陳慧嫻的女生住在華富村第八座，自升讀中學以來引來了不少男生的追求，但最終她戀上了一個長得像來到日本開餐廳的中年日本男人。少女打算在18歲時追給她心中的白馬王子，但他卻在她18歲生日時提出分手，就在當晚她穿著打算在謝師宴時穿著的紅色禮服在瀑布灣跳河自盡。<br />\n<br />\n自此，每到晚上12時來到瀑布灣的男生都會看到一個漂亮清秀的少女，要是拒絕了她的誘惑你與自己伴侶將會白頭到老，但要是頂不住她的誘惑你將你陳屍在瀑布灣中。<br />\n<br />\n根據村內的人所說，這是對男士忠貞的考驗。<br />\n<br />\n只要挺得過誘惑，才會是自己值得廝守一生的伴侶,而這更是女生間的秘密，對於那班始亂終棄的賤男來說，他們根本沒有活在世人的不必要。<br />\n<br />\n這晚凌晨，29歲的OL小桃約了拍了拖4年半的男友Jason前來瀑布灣約會&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e8cbb1a566f38b57372732667135baf76990e365","tid":2076596,"uid":49462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeda7026d83a854ead5a39952a565c2f24d80f32","tid":2076596,"uid":281374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">About me:</span><br />\n下流編劇一名，剛開始學習繪畫，喜歡既朋友可以Follow同Like我既FB page同ig <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">IG: </span><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/akihokurosawa/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fakihokurosawa%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JfrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=6e73247c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagr